<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Founders' Agreement Template</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; line-height: 1.6; margin: 40px; }
        .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .parties { border: 1px solid #000; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .section { margin: 25px 0; }
        .clause { margin: 15px 0; }
        .signature-block { margin-top: 40px; border-top: 1px solid #000; padding-top: 20px; }
        .fill-in { border-bottom: 1px solid #000; min-width: 200px; }
        h1 { font-size: 18px; text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase; }
        h2 { font-size: 16px; margin-top: 30px; }
        h3 { font-size: 14px; margin-top: 20px; }
        .checkbox { display: inline-block; width: 15px; height: 15px; border: 1px solid #000; margin-right: 5px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>FOUNDERS' AGREEMENT</h1>
        <h2>Between Two Co-Founders</h2>
        <p><strong>Comprehensive Legal Framework for Startup Co-Founders</strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="parties">
        <p><strong>THIS FOUNDERS' AGREEMENT</strong> is made on this <span class="fill-in">___</span> day of <span class="fill-in">_______</span>, 2024, between:</p>
        
        <p><strong>FOUNDER 1:</strong></p>
        <p>Name: <span class="fill-in">________________________</span></p>
        <p>Address: <span class="fill-in">_____________________</span></p>
        <p><span class="fill-in">_____________________________</span></p>
        <p>Email: <span class="fill-in">_______________________</span></p>
        <p>Phone: <span class="fill-in">______________________</span></p>
        <p>PAN: <span class="fill-in">________________________</span></p>

        <p><strong>FOUNDER 2:</strong></p>
        <p>Name: <span class="fill-in">________________________</span></p>
        <p>Address: <span class="fill-in">_____________________</span></p>
        <p><span class="fill-in">_____________________________</span></p>
        <p>Email: <span class="fill-in">_______________________</span></p>
        <p>Phone: <span class="fill-in">______________________</span></p>
        <p>PAN: <span class="fill-in">________________________</span></p>

        <p><strong>COMPANY DETAILS:</strong></p>
        <p>Proposed Company Name: <span class="fill-in">________________</span></p>
        <p>Business Description: <span class="fill-in">__________________</span></p>
        <p>Registered Office: <span class="fill-in">____________________</span></p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>1. EQUITY ALLOCATION AND VESTING</h2>
        
        <div class="clause">
            <h3>1.1 Initial Equity Split</h3>
            <p>• <strong>Founder 1</strong>: <span class="fill-in">___</span>% of total equity shares</p>
            <p>• <strong>Founder 2</strong>: <span class="fill-in">___</span>% of total equity shares</p>
            <p>• <strong>Employee Stock Option Pool</strong>: <span class="fill-in">___</span>% (to be created)</p>
            <p>• <strong>Future Investor Pool</strong>: <span class="fill-in">___</span>% (reserved)</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h3>1.2 Vesting Schedule</h3>
            <p>• <strong>Vesting Period</strong>: 4 years</p>
            <p>• <strong>Cliff Period</strong>: 1 year (25% vests after 1 year)</p>
            <p>• <strong>Accelerated Vesting</strong>: Monthly vesting of 1/48th of shares after cliff</p>
            <p>• <strong>Trigger Events</strong>:</p>
            <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;- Single Trigger: Change of control</p>
            <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;- Double Trigger: Change of control + involuntary termination</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>2. ROLES AND RESPONSIBILITIES</h2>
        
        <div class="clause">
            <h3>2.1 Founder 1 - [Title: e.g., CEO/CTO]</h3>
            <p><strong>Primary Responsibilities:</strong></p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Overall business strategy and vision</p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Fundraising and investor relations</p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Board and shareholder management</p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Legal and compliance oversight</p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Partnership and business development</p>
            
            <p><strong>Key Metrics/KPIs:</strong></p>
            <p>• Revenue targets: ₹<span class="fill-in">_______</span> annually</p>
            <p>• Customer acquisition: <span class="fill-in">_____</span> customers</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h3>2.2 Founder 2 - [Title: e.g., CTO/CMO]</h3>
            <p><strong>Primary Responsibilities:</strong></p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Product development and technology</p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Engineering team management</p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Technical architecture decisions</p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Quality assurance and testing</p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Security and infrastructure</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>3. DECISION MAKING MATRIX</h2>
        
        <div class="clause">
            <h3>3.1 Unanimous Consent Required</h3>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Raising external funding above ₹<span class="fill-in">______</span></p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Sale or merger of the Company</p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Major pivots or business model changes</p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Creating employee stock option pools</p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Hiring/firing C-level executives</p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Taking debt above ₹<span class="fill-in">______</span></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>4. INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY</h2>
        
        <div class="clause">
            <h3>4.1 IP Assignment</h3>
            <p>All intellectual property created by either Founder relating to the Company's business shall be automatically assigned to the Company. Each Founder represents that they have full rights to assign all IP contributed.</p>
            
            <h3>4.2 Pre-Existing IP</h3>
            <p><strong>Founder 1 Pre-Existing IP:</strong></p>
            <p><span class="fill-in">________________________</span></p>
            <p><strong>License to Company</strong>: [Exclusive/Non-exclusive/None]</p>
            
            <p><strong>Founder 2 Pre-Existing IP:</strong></p>
            <p><span class="fill-in">________________________</span></p>
            <p><strong>License to Company</strong>: [Exclusive/Non-exclusive/None]</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>5. NON-COMPETE AND NON-SOLICITATION</h2>
        
        <div class="clause">
            <h3>5.1 Non-Compete (During Employment)</h3>
            <p>Each Founder agrees not to:</p>
            <p>• Engage in competing business activities</p>
            <p>• Provide services to direct competitors</p>
            <p>• Develop competing products or services</p>
            <p>• Solicit Company employees or customers</p>
            
            <h3>5.2 Non-Solicitation (12 months post-exit)</h3>
            <p>• Not solicit Company employees for competing businesses</p>
            <p>• Not solicit Company customers or clients</p>
            <p>• Not use confidential information for competing purposes</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>6. FOUNDER DEPARTURE</h2>
        
        <div class="clause">
            <h3>6.1 Voluntary Departure</h3>
            <p><strong>Good Reason Resignation</strong> (treated as involuntary):</p>
            <p>• Material reduction in duties or responsibilities</p>
            <p>• Reduction in compensation by >20%</p>
            <p>• Material breach of this Agreement by other Founder</p>
            
            <h3>6.2 Involuntary Departure</h3>
            <p><strong>For Cause Termination:</strong></p>
            <p>• Willful misconduct or gross negligence</p>
            <p>• Material breach of fiduciary duties</p>
            <p>• Violation of non-compete or confidentiality</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>7. DISPUTE RESOLUTION</h2>
        
        <div class="clause">
            <h3>7.1 Escalation Process</h3>
            <p>1. <strong>Direct Discussion</strong>: 30-day good faith negotiation</p>
            <p>2. <strong>Mediation</strong>: Binding mediation with neutral third party</p>
            <p>3. <strong>Arbitration</strong>: ICC Arbitration Rules, New Delhi seat</p>
            <p>4. <strong>Court Jurisdiction</strong>: Delhi High Court (if arbitration fails)</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="signature-block">
        <h2>EXECUTION</h2>
        
        <table width="100%">
            <tr>
                <td width="50%">
                    <p><strong>FOUNDER 1:</strong></p>
                    <br><br>
                    <p>Signature: ________________________</p>
                    <p>Name: ____________________________</p>
                    <p>Date: ____________________________</p>
                </td>
                <td width="50%">
                    <p><strong>FOUNDER 2:</strong></p>
                    <br><br>
                    <p>Signature: ________________________</p>
                    <p>Name: ____________________________</p>
                    <p>Date: ____________________________</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <br><br>
        <p><strong>WITNESSES:</strong></p>
        <table width="100%">
            <tr>
                <td width="50%">
                    <p>Witness 1:</p>
                    <p>Signature: ________________________</p>
                    <p>Name: ____________________________</p>
                    <p>Date: ____________________________</p>
                </td>
                <td width="50%">
                    <p>Witness 2:</p>
                    <p>Signature: ________________________</p>
                    <p>Name: ____________________________</p>
                    <p>Date: ____________________________</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 40px; border-top: 2px solid #000; padding-top: 20px;">
        <p><strong>IMPORTANT LEGAL DISCLAIMER:</strong></p>
        <p>This is a template document for educational purposes. Please consult qualified legal counsel before executing any agreement. Laws vary by jurisdiction and individual circumstances.</p>
        
        <p><strong>Template Source:</strong> The Indian Startup - P5 Legal Stack<br>
        <strong>Version:</strong> 2.0 | <strong>Last Updated:</strong> December 2024<br>
        <strong>Jurisdiction:</strong> India | <strong>Language:</strong> English</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>